title: Dario Potroško
text:
Dario Potroško (born 9 October 1992) is a <a href="Croatia">Croatia</a>n <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for Austrian club TUS Vorau.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Austrian%20Football%20First%20League">Austrian Football First League</a> debut for <a href="Kapfenberger%20SV">Kapfenberger SV</a> on 4 August 2017 in a game against <a href="WSG%20Wattens">WSG Wattens</a>.
Ahead of the 2019-20 season, Potroško joined TUS Vorau.
